### Q5. Does F4 behave as a stressor across C bins?

**Yes, with strong C-bin dependence.** F4_nonzero rate per fixture-local tercile:

| Fixture | T1_small_radicand | T2_intermediate_radicand | T3_large_radicand |
|---|---|---|---|
